{
  "text": "Statistical analysis of baroreflex data was performed using a Bayesian multi-level model [CITATION_1] to estimate the daily effects of global HI and MAPC treatment under hypoxic and sham conditions on the baroreflex sensitivity. This model corrects for repeated measurements and takes into account variance between and within subjects [CITATION_2] . Statistical time series analysis was conducted using the Stan for R package (version 2.6.0) in R (version 3.1.1).",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "62610127",
    "[CITATION_2]": "62610127"
